snippet.title: Nope Challenge - Official Trailer | Upload VR Showcase Winter 2023
snippet.description: Watch the trailer for Nope Challenge to discover what this upcoming VR game is all about--and it's probably exactly as you imagined. The trailer showcases various terrifying tests you can challenge yourself to, like coming face to face with spiders, scary clowns, and more. However, if it becomes too much for you to handle, you can press a button to "nope" out of a scary situation. Nope Challenge will be available in April 2024 on Meta Quest.
